headline: Parks Associates Announces the 2025 Property Innovation Awards Nominations
summary: International research firm Parks Associates today announced the current nominees for the 2025 Property Innovation Awards, which recognizes properties and teams leading in proptech innovation. Winners will be awarded at Smart Spaces, September 16-17 at the HALL Arts Hotel in Dallas, Texas.
